text: Edurne is the first studio album by Edurne, released by Epic Records on March 21, 2006 in Spain. On September 26, a reissue of the album was released, including the previously unreleased track Te falta veneno (Yo soy Bea) and two remixes of Despierta. == __LEAD_SECTION__ == Edurne is the first studio album by Edurne, released by Epic Records on March 21, 2006 in Spain.
